        "created_at": "2020-01-14T08:45:21.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com/wine.asp?iWine=3023973\"><strong>2017 Pierre-Yves Colin-Morey Chassagne-Montrachet 1er Cru Les Caillerets</strong></a> <em>- France, Burgundy, C\u00f4te de Beaune, Chassagne-Montrachet 1er Cru (1/14/2020)</em><br>\nA great nose of flinty, smoky mineral, white peach and aniseed. It is intense, linear and powerful, with great drive and cut. The finish is long and laden with chalky dry extract and a big squeeze of citrus.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"https://www.cellartracker.com\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>",
