        "name": "J0zef P1nxten",
        "username": "Jozef.P",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/jozef.p/{size}/1239_2.png",
        "created_at": "2020-01-14T16:21:52.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Do all of you feel that there is a difference between his estate and negoce bottlings? I drink them from time to time, but am not familiar with the distinction for him, as it\u2019s not that clear from the bottles. I am quite sensitive to this for red wines, but have the feeling it matters less in the market for white wines?</p>",
